loading="lazy"
alt="AWS Authentication"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="199"
data-flex-basis="479px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Obtain and configure your Access Key ID and Secret Access Key from the AWS console.
Once configured, AWS resources should appear in AWS Explorer.&lt;br>
