>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Select Create Lambda Function and input the necessary values.&lt;br>
For the Handler, enter &lt;code>&amp;lt;filename&amp;gt;.&amp;lt;function name&amp;gt;&lt;/code> from your code snippet.&lt;br>
